{"tid":1423701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出文宣向市民解釋光復香港時代革命啊！","createTime":"2019-08-06T14:42:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T18:20:45.000Z","uid":284436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96a8b2c7cb43c4c6ca2b07bd8f3331bfc08fe084","tid":1423701,"uid":284436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:42:24.000Z","msg":"有冇文宣可以出宣言講清楚光復香港咩？革新香港咩？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好比政府spin做港獨</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重新五大訴求</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d32f8cefba6f33f6af71a589078fafb70c0dc1e9","tid":1423701,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"不要說「黑社會」，試著說「政治工具」"},{"pid":"0a8ee64e670579911c400fb76acfdfc898984a73","tid":1423701,"uid":280349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:42:50.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n「緊急號外」紅底理論upgrade 左，要拆解一下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422647\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422647</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fe24ac2bcb06dc79ede04359e8d2579d5f8777ff","tid":1423701,"uid":280847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T14:43:47.000Z","msg":"黑社會"},{"pid":"ef51f63bbc8c2ba1afdc5a7d9cbcea013b04c531","tid":1423701,"uid":37232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T18:20:45.000Z","msg":"其中一個方向係<br />\n正名「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n光復香港 = 回復以往繁榮既香港<br />\n方法: 首4大訴求<br />\n一、徹底撤回逃犯條例的修訂，以至法理上終止條例程序<br />\n二、收回612暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷對之前及今後所有反送中抗爭者控罪 <br />\n四、成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警察濫權<br />\n<br />\n時代革命=香港體制要改革<br />\n方法: 第五大訴求<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行真正的雙普選<br />\n<br />\n而唔係林鄭所誤解既港獨<br />\n<br />\n建議之一, 請其他巴打更改<br />\n<br />\n重溫 616, 71, 721 宣言, 文宣請加油, 令我們的行動合理<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1423473\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1423473</a>"}]}